      "stem_html": "Propose a structure for an aromatic hydrocarbon, C<sub>11</sub>H<sub>16</sub>, that has the following <sup>13</sup>C NMR spectral data:\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n<li>Broadband decoupled: 29.5, 31.8, 50.2, 125.5, 127.5, 130.3, 139.8 <i>δ</i></li>\n<li>DEPT-90: 125.5, 127.5, 130.3 <i>δ</i></li>\n<li>DEPT-135: positive peaks at 29.5, 125.5, 127.5, 130.3 <i>δ;</i> negative peak at 50.2 <i>δ</i></li>\n</ul>",
